# E2E Regression Tests

This directory contains story-specific E2E tests that have been archived after story completion.

When `/finish-story` runs, story-specific tests (e.g., `e2e/story-e01-s03.spec.ts`) are moved here to:
1. Prevent them from running in every test suite (they're already validated)
2. Keep them as regression tests for future reference
3. Maintain a history of story-specific test coverage

Tests in this directory are not run by default but can be executed manually or as part of extended regression suites.
